commit.message:
Duplicate all the things!

Hackathon timing in play now. Rather than mess with getting everything
cleaner with script variables, just duplicate things like textures and
materials to make sure nothing conflicts.

Also lower resolution of video playback. It isn't noticed on device and
makes it run smoother.

Cleanup the scripts and assets

This should make it easier to start reproducing them.

scene: Update values for ML Image Tracker & Tracking Cube

Setting "Longer Dimension In Scene Units" to the size of the long edge
of the poster makes the tracking much better.

Also tweak the cube size for debugging.

Defaults: Default to showing the demo only

We don't want the tracking cube or axis stuff for now
